article.description: — Ethan Price had 20 points in Eastern Washington's 85-70 victory against Northern Arizona on Saturday night.
article.headline: Eastern Washington defeats Northern Arizona 85-70
article.story: CHENEY, Wash. -- — Ethan Price had 20 points in Eastern Washington's 85-70 victory against Northern Arizona on Saturday night. Price added five rebounds for the Eagles (13-7, 7-0 Big Sky Conference). Cedric Coward scored 15 points and added five rebounds. Casey Jones was 4-of-4 shooting and 5 of 9 from the free-throw line to finish with 13 points. The Eagles extended their winning streak to nine games. Carson Basham finished with 22 points and nine rebounds for the Lumberjacks (10-11, 3-4). Northern Arizona also got 14 points and six assists from Jayden Jackson. Oakland Fort also had 11 points and four steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
